SpotiApp will download your playlists from Apple Music, Deezer, Google, Youtube and other popular music applications to Spotify.

START:
- go to any service that has a playlist you need;
- take a screenshot;
- upload a screenshot to SpotiApp;
- SpotiApp recognizes your music tracks by picture;
- click "Transfer to Spotify" - the list will be saved in Spotify under "Favorite tracks";
- enjoy!

Under UAE Labour Law, employees are entitled to end of service gratuities (severance pay).

UAE Gratuity Calculator has been developed in accordance with UAE Labour Law to allow you to calculate gratuity for limited and unlimited contracts with end of service options.

It is important to calculate your end of service gratuities to ensure you are paid the correct amount due.

UAE Gratuity Calculator will help you to:
 - Financially plan your future;
 - Identify any errors made by your company;
 - Calculate gratuity for limited and unlimited contracts;
 - Understand the gratuity calculation process.
